%%time

tree = os.walk(os.getcwd())
global_freqdict = {}
file_names = []
short_files_rule = re.compile('\.txt$')
for files in tree:
    if re.search('Genres$', files[0]) != None:
        for folder in files[1]:
            global_freqdict[folder] = {}
    if re.search('Genres\\\([A-Za-z_]+)$', files[0]) != None:
        current_genre = re.search('Genres\\\([A-Za-z_]+)$', files[0]).group(1)
        print('Starting to work on: '+current_genre)
        bigrams_dict, trigrams_dict = {}, {}
        files_counter = 0

        random_files = random.sample(files[2], len(files[2]))
        print('Random sample created.')
        
        tokens_counter = 0
        break_crawler = False
        for file in random_files:
            if break_crawler == True:
                break
            if short_files_rule.search(file) != None:
                if files_counter != 0 and files_counter%50 == 0:
                    print(str(files_counter)+' files processed...')
                files_counter += 1

                file_name = os.path.join(files[0], file)
                file = open(file_name, 'r', encoding='utf-8').read()
                all_tokens = nltk.word_tokenize(file)
                
                tokens, sentence_tokens = [], []
                for token in all_tokens:
                    if re.search('^[--\-]+$', token) != None and token != '-':
                        sentence_tokens.append(token)
                        tokens_counter += 1
                    if re.search('^[\.!\?]$', token) != None:
                        if sentence_tokens != []:
                            tokens.append(sentence_tokens)
                            sentence_tokens = []
                    if tokens_counter > 1000000:
                        print(str(tokens_counter) + '/1000000 tokens done.')
                        break_crawler = True
                        break
                
                for sentence in tokens:
                    pos_tagged_text = nltk.pos_tag(sentence, lang='rus')
                    for index in range(len(pos_tagged_text)):
                        if index != len(pos_tagged_text)-1:
                            this_pos = re.sub('=.+', '', pos_tagged_text[index][1])
                            next_pos = re.sub('=.+', '', pos_tagged_text[index+1][1])
                            bigram = (this_pos, next_pos)
                            bigrams_dict[bigram] = bigrams_dict.get(bigram, 0) + 1
        global_freqdict[current_genre] = bigrams_dict

plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))
layout = nx.spring_layout
region = 330
for genre, freq_dict in global_freqdict.items():
    G=nx.Graph(name = genre)
    G.add_edges_from(freq_dict.keys())
    pos = layout(G)
    region += 1
    plt.subplot(region)    
    plt.title(genre)
    nx.draw(G, pos, node_size=10, with_labels=False)
    nx.write_gml(G, genre+'_graph.gml')
    print(nx.info(G)+'\r\n')
plt.show()

    GW=nx.Graph()
    for x, y in sorted(freq_dict.items()): 
        GW.add_edge(x[0],x[1],weight=y)
    AW = nx.adjacency_matrix(GW)
    #print(genre)
    #print (AW.todense())
    
    df =nx.to_pandas_dataframe(GW)
    pos = layout(GW)

for genre, freq_dict in global_freqdict.items():
    GW=nx.Graph()
    all_edges = sum(freq_dict.values())    
    for x, y in sorted(freq_dict.items()): 
        GW.add_edge(x[0],x[1],weight=(y/all_edges)*100)    
        
    print(genre)
    print ('Diameter: ', nx.diameter(GW))
    print ('Center: ', nx.center(GW))
    if nx.center(GW) != nx.periphery(GW):
        print ('Periphery: ', nx.periphery(GW))
        
    print ('Triangles: ', sum(nx.triangles(GW).values())/3)
    print ('Average clustering: ', nx.average_clustering(GW))
    print ('Transitivity: ', nx.transitivity(GW))
    
    print('\n')

layout = nx.spring_layout
region = 330
for genre, freq_dict in global_freqdict.items():
    GW=nx.Graph()
    for x, y in sorted(freq_dict.items()): 
        GW.add_edge(x[0],x[1],weight=y)
    dcent = nx.degree_centrality(GW)
    #print(genre)
    #print(sorted(dcent.items(),reverse=True,key = itemgetter(1)))
    sizes = [x*4000 for x in dcent.values()]
    colors = [float(x) for x in dcent.values()]
    pos = layout(GW)
    region += 1
    plt.subplot(region)
    plt.title(genre)
    plt.axis('off')
    nx.draw_networkx(GW,with_labels=True,node_size=sizes,node_color = colors,cmap = plt.cm.winter,alpha=0.9)
plt.savefig('degree_centrality.png')

for genre, freq_dict in global_freqdict.items():
    print(genre)
    GW=nx.Graph()
    for x, y in sorted(freq_dict.items()): 
        GW.add_edge(x[0],x[1],weight=y)
    dcent = nx.degree_centrality(GW)
    bcent=nx.betweenness_centrality(GW)
    ccent=nx.closeness_centrality(GW)
    ecent=nx.eigenvector_centrality_numpy(GW)
    df2=pd.DataFrame(data=[dcent,bcent,ccent,ecent]).transpose()
    df2.columns=['Degree centrality','Betweenness centrality','Closensess centrality', 'Eigencentrality']
    df2.sort_values('Eigencentrality', ascending=False, inplace=True)
    print(df2, '\n')
    df2.to_csv(genre+'_centralities.csv')

plt.figure(figsize=(30,30))
layout = nx.spring_layout
region = 330
for genre, freq_dict in global_freqdict.items():
    GW=nx.Graph()
    for x, y in sorted(freq_dict.items()): 
        GW.add_edge(x[0],x[1],weight=y)
    GW.remove_edges_from(nx.selfloop_edges(GW))
    
    colors = [float(x) for x in freq_dict.values()]
    cores=nx.core_number(GW)
    pos = layout(GW)
    region += 1
    plt.subplot(region)
    plt.title(genre)
    nx.draw(GW, with_labels=True, node_color=list(cores.values()), node_size=5000, cmap = plt.get_cmap('terrain'), alpha=0.8)
plt.savefig('core.png')
plt.show()
